====Noun====
'''gib'''
# A [[bolt]] or [[wedge]] made from [[wood]] or [[metal]] used for holding a [[machine]] part in [[place]].

====Transitive verb====
'''to gib''' ('''past tense and past participle:''' ''gibbed'')
